comments: McDaniels (CHA) makes marginal contact with Barton's (DEN) non-shooting arm during his driving shot attempt.
Campazzo (DEN) places his hand to Rozier's (CHA) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Barton (DEN) makes incidental contact with Washington's (CHA) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) moves into Washington's (CHA) space off ball and the contact should be deemed marginal.
Jokic (DEN) briefly places his arm against McDaniels' (CHA) body off ball and disengages.
Green (DEN) briefly places his hand to Washington's (CHA) front at the start of his drive and immediately slides his hand off.
Campazzo (DEN) grabs and pulls Washington's (CHA) arm and affects his ability to defend the play.
Smith (CHA) dislodges the ball from Jokic (DEN) defending his driving shot attempt before incidental contact occurs.
Washington (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in Barton's (DEN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Jokic (DEN) places his hand to Rozier's (CHA) back during the pick and releases away from the contact.
Morris (DEN) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
Campazzo (DEN) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Barton (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Washington's (CHA) path and does not deliver contact.
Green (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Smith's (CHA) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
McDaniels (CHA) makes marginal contact with Morris' (DEN) body after the release his jump shot attempt.
